data.title: Whitney Houston’s ‘Miracle’ Was Released On This Day In 1991
data.meta_description: Released on this day 33 years ago (April 16, 1991), "Miracle" was the third single from Whitney's 'I'm Your Baby Tonight' album. Written and produced by L.A. Reid and Babyface, the single reached #9 on the Billboard Hot 100, #2 on the Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs chart and #4 on the Adult Contemporary chart.
